-| Item             | Typical Routing                      | Watch For                             |
-| ---------------- | ------------------------------------ | ------------------------------------- |
-| Overdrafts       | Cash (netted) or Debt                | Double-count if in both               |
-| Accrued interest | Indebtedness                         | Could be in WC accrued liabilities    |
-| Deal bonuses     | Transaction Expenses                 | Could be in Indebtedness or WC        |
-| Tax payables     | Working Capital                      | Sometimes excluded entirely           |
-| Deferred revenue | Working Capital                      | Sometimes in Indebtedness (long-term) |
-| Severance        | Transaction Expenses or Indebtedness | Routing must be explicit              |
